<div class="text-container"><span class="t s3" style="left:248px;bottom:537px;letter-spacing:-0.14px;word-spacing:0.05px;">UML Class Diagram </span>
<span class="t s2" style="left:1068px;bottom:18px;">4 </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:427px;letter-spacing:0.09px;word-spacing:0.02px;">This Diagram illustrates the service- </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:405px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">oriented backend architecture of the </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:383px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.02px;">GAD system. The central BackendApp </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:361px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.02px;">orchestrates specialized services— </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:339px;letter-spacing:0.09px;word-spacing:0.02px;">including the ExternalAPIService for </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:317px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">data gathering, RiskCalculationService </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:295px;letter-spacing:0.09px;word-spacing:0.02px;">for hazard assessment, and </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:273px;letter-spacing:0.09px;word-spacing:0.01px;">DatabaseService for persistence. These </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:251px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">services interact with underlying </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:229px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">database entities like Analysis, State, </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:207px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">and NRICounty to generate, store, and </span>
<span class="t sa" data-mappings='[[30,"fi"]]' style="left:806px;bottom:185px;letter-spacing:0.1px;word-spacing:0.01px;">export location-based risk proﬁles and </span>
<span class="t sa" style="left:806px;bottom:163px;letter-spacing:0.11px;word-spacing:0.02px;">construction recommendations </span></div>

